<item>
            <title>[LU-2806] Build Lustre with OFED 3.5 </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2806</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;(Official) Openfabrics release notes states that nodes running kernel 2.6.32-279 and RedHat EL6.3 are only supported by OFED release 3.5-rc&lt;/p&gt;
{1,2,3,4,5,6}
&lt;p&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Since lbuild suppress download of OFED release candidates a small code change inside the script will disable this feature and allow the compilation of Lustre against the OFED release canditate(s).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The changes will allow to test OFED-3.5, and will be removed as soon as a stable version of OFED-3.5(or later) is going to be available. The change WON&apos;T be landed in any branch.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
